---
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import engranajeMano from "../../assets/engranaje-sobre-mano.png";
import engranajeImg from "../../assets/engranaje.png";
import pincelImg from "../../assets/pincel.png";
import escalaImg from "../../assets/escala-sin-lim.png";
---

<section class="bg-gray-100 pt-16 lg:pt-24 pb-0 font-body">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 md:divide-x-2 divide-gray-500"
        >
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-6 px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-8 md:py-0"
            >
                <div
                    class="relative w-32 h-32 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                >
                    <Image
                        src={engranajeMano}
                        alt="Enfoque personalizado"
                        class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
                <p
                    class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm lg:text-base text-justify font-semibold flex-grow"
                >
                    Ofrecemos un enfoque altamente personalizado, trabajando
                    estrechamente con cada cliente para entender a fondo sus
                    necesidades y crear soluciones tecnológicas que realmente se
                    adapten a sus procesos y objetivos específicos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-6 px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-8 md:py-0 border-t-2 md:border-t-0 border-gray-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="relative w-32 h-32 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                >
                    <Image
                        src={engranajeImg}
                        alt="Resiliencia operativa"
                        class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
                <p
                    class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm lg:text-base text-justify font-semibold flex-grow"
                >
                    Más allá de entregar soluciones tecnológicas, nos centramos
                    en fortalecer la resiliencia operativa y digital de nuestros
                    clientes, ayudándoles a adaptarse rápidamente a los cambios
                    del mercado y superar desafíos inesperados.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-6 px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-8 md:py-0 border-t-2 md:border-t-0 border-gray-300"
            >
                <div
                    class="relative w-32 h-32 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                >
                    <Image
                        src={pincelImg}
                        alt="Metodologías ágiles"
                        class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
                <p
                    class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm lg:text-base text-justify font-semibold flex-grow"
                >
                    Aplicamos metodologías ágiles que nos permiten ser
                    flexibles, adaptarnos rápidamente a cambios y entregar
                    productos de calidad en plazos más cortos, manteniendo al
                    cliente involucrado en cada etapa del desarrollo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pt-8 lg:pt-12">
        <Image
            src={escalaImg}
            alt="Escala sin límites"
            class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
        />
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 flex items-end justify-end pr-4 md:pr-8 lg:pr-16 pb-4 md:pb-6"
        >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-2 md:gap-3">
                <Button
                    variant="primary"
                    href="#cotizar"
                    size="none"
                    class="mr-20 translate-y-6 lg:translate-y-0 py-2 px-4 md:py-2.5 md:px-6 text-[6px] md:text-xs lg:text-sm xl:text-base"
                >
                    Quiero mi cotización
                </Button>

                <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                        <svg
                            class="w-3 h-3 md:w-4 md:h-4 text-white"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span
                            class="text-white font-heading text-xs md:text-lg font-normal"
                            >Arenalogix</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                        <svg
                            class="w-3 h-3 md:w-4 md:h-4 text-white"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span
                            class="text-white font-heading text-xs md:text-lg font-normal"
                            >Arenalogix</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
